_explanation-text"> Since i is static variable, it is shared among all calls to main().  So is reduced by 1 by every function call.</div></div></div><div class="mtq_question mtq_scroll_item-1" id="mtq_question-4-1"><table class="mtq_question_heading_table"><tr><td><div class="mtq_question_label ">Question 4</div><div id="mtq_stamp-4-1" class="mtq_stamp"></div></td></tr></table><div id="mtq_question_text-4-1" class="mtq_question_text"><pre class="brush: cpp; title: ; notranslate" title="">
