 17 Explanation: </div><div class="mtq_explanation-text"> Note that ptr is a pointer to a constant.  So value pointed cannot be changed using the pointer ptr.  See <a target="_blank">Const Qualifier in C</a> for more details.</div></div></div><div class="mtq_question mtq_scroll_item-1" id="mtq_question-18-1"><table class="mtq_question_heading_table"><tr><td><div class="mtq_question_label ">Question 18</div><div id="mtq_stamp-18-1" class="mtq_stamp"></div></td></tr></table><div id="mtq_question_text-18-1" class="mtq_question_text">Output of following program

